sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant App as React App
    participant Server as Node.js Server
    participant OCR as Google Vision API
    participant Socket as WebSocket
    
    User->>App: Upload Receipt Image
    App->>Server: POST /upload
    Server->>OCR: Send Image
    OCR-->>Server: Return Extracted Text
    Server->>Server: Parse Items & Prices
    Server-->>App: Return Bill Data
    User->>App: Create Session
    App->>Socket: Join Room
    loop Real-time Updates
        User->>App: Claim Item
        App->>Socket: Emit "claim" event
        Socket->>OtherUsers: Broadcast Update
    end